FailAt 21

Echo "This icon copies the contents of the current"
Echo "drawer to a QDOS-formatted floppy in drive 0"
Echo " "

Assign >NIL: QL0: EXISTS

If WARN
 Echo "Please mount the QLfilesystem and try again."
 Echo "For instructions see Amiga Qdos installation."
 Wait 5
Else
 QLFormat -u0 -mBUSY -a
 DiskChange QL0:
 COPY ~(#?.info) QL0:
 Relabel QL0: CharMoDemo
EndIf
